Note: Because the effects of the Rainstick are much less than what is actually stated in-game, you are likely better off increasing the value of drone rewards over increasing the odds of receiving bocks. For example, while a Legendary Meggnificent (T4L) Carved Rainstick will guarantee Bocks rewards, a Common Jeweled (T3C) Aurelian Brooch will double the value of received rewards. In other words, the Legendary Rainstick will increase your earned Bocks by approximately 43% while a T3C Brooch will increase your Bocks earnings by 50%. Thus, you are usually better off equipping an Aurelian Brooch, a Mercury's Lens, a Neodymium Medallion and/or a Vial of Martian Dust before equipping a Rainstick. Compare the Actual Bock Income Increase in the chart above to your other artifacts to determine which is the best choice for you.

