Challenges (formerly called Missions) are in-game quests that will reward you with Bocks, Soul Eggs, or Golden Eggs when you meet the requirements of your current Challenge. Challenges do not reset upon upgrade or Prestige and some can be completed in a contract farm.

There is a bar at the bottom of the Challenges box which displays your progress through all of the Challenges. Trophies replace Challenges when all are completed.



