Trivia
Egg laying challenges are cumulative - they do not need to be done all in one prestige.
Drone takedown challenges do not carry over between challenges. The game will store a 'referenceValue' when you start the challenge, and will start counting from there. This means that adding all of the drone challenges will in total require 180 drones tapped.
Cash rewards are often visually cut off on smaller devices.
You cannot complete the Soul King challenge solely through previous challenges - some kind of calendar reward/prestige/contract reward must be obtained.
