Eggfinity Stones (often called Stones for short) are items in Egg, Inc. introduced in Version 1.20 alongside Artifacts and Ingredients. They are one possible reward from launching Spaceships. Fragments of these Stones can be obtained by consuming certain Artifacts, e.g. consuming Lunar Totems gives Lunar Stone Fragments to the player. These fragments will consume to uncapped piggy fill.

Certain Artifacts have sockets, and players can put Stones inside these sockets to enhance the effects of Artifacts. The first tier of each Stone is a Fragment. Stone Fragments cannot be placed inside sockets as they do not provide any bonuses. Stone Fragments must be used in the Hall of Artifacts in order to craft higher tier Stones.

