Stone Crafting
Main article: Crafting

Stone fragments will add uncapped fill to the Piggy Bank. Tier 2 and higher stones can be consumed for Golden Eggs, and you can generally craft a stone of a higher tier with enough stones of the lower tier, plus some Golden Eggs. If you craft enough to get their Golden Egg costs down, the following three stones will run you a Golden Egg profit when you craft the T1s into T2, then consume the T2: Lunar, Shell, Tachyon. No other stone (or artifact) exhibits this behaviour, even after 300 crafts (which reduces the crafting cost to the lowest it will ever be).

