Types of Stones
Clarity Stone
Clarity Stones enable the effect of the host Artifact to work on the Enlightenment Egg. Because you can use Eggceptional Clarity Stones to get an artifact up to 300% (x3) effectiveness, even after you get the Enlightenment Diamond, these are very useful on Medallions and Brooches to farm Golden Eggs on an Enlightenment Farm. Note that Clarity Stones may behave counterintuitively, because the game's math is not written correctly. In particular, an artifact providing a multiplicative effect is never actually doing that - it provides an additive effect instead. E.g. x10 is really +900%, and +200% is +200%, not x3. This will mess up your intuition on stacked Clarity Stones, especially on those artifacts that list multiplicative factors; for example, 4 T4 Clarities (an x3 effect) would modify +900 to +2700 and +200 to +600 - i.e. x10 becomes x27 and x3 becomes x7.

