Dilithium Stone
Dilithium Stones increase boost duration. When a boost is consumed, all Dilithium Stones impact its duration, and then the stones are never checked again; this means you should make yourself a "Dilithium Set" of artifacts with as many slots as possible devoted to Dilithium Stones, without caring about what the artifacts actually do. This will let you equip the Dilithium Set, use boosts, and then swap to a set of relevant artifacts, keeping the duration buff from the Dilithium Stones. Dilithium stones stack multiplicatively, i.e. as advertised: the duration multiplier of 2 T4 Dilithium stones is 1.08 × 1.08 = 1.1664.

