Fill the Tank with at least 24TDark Matter Egg}}Darkmatter Eggs (see chart below). This will let you launch up to 4 ships while refilling the other Eggs.
Use the remaining Tank space to store as many Tachyon Egg}}Tachyon, Dilithium Egg}}Dilithium, andAntimatter Egg}}Antimatter Eggs as possible (based on your Tank level below).
