Max out your tank with Tachyon, then halve the amount twice
Fuel and abandon 6 extended henerprises to discard 6T Tachyon Eggs
Fill your tank with Dilithium Eggs
Fuel and abandon 8 short henerprises to discard 16T dilithium eggs
Fill your fuel tank with Dark Matter
Fuel and abandon 14 short henerprises
Fill your tank with Antimatter
Fuel and abandon 2 standard voyeggers
Fill your tank with Rocket Fuel
Again - you refuel 30T eggs every 3 days which can be done passively without boosting, you get exthens on tap every 3 days if you do refill properly and can also launch unlimited chicken heavies with the rocket fuel eggs!

Switch on Weekends
By @pianoman24 (358769030204751874)

6T Tachyon
54T Dilithium
36T Antimatter
4T Dark Matter
This tank setup allows you to fuel 6 rockets per week and _switch your tank only once per weekend (during prestige events) for at least 10 weeks straight! The beauty of this is you only have to switch your farm when you would want to switch it anyway to prestige and you don't have to think about it during the week. This setup was found by painstakingly searching through every mathematically unique setup and ranking them based on multiple variables. Trust me, this is the best out there.

NOTE: This only works if you have most of the FTL improvements epic research (the one that makes the later missions take less time.) Otherwise each 6-mission set takes longer than a week.

Here are three rules-of-thumb to follow:

1. Launch no more than 6 rockets on a single farm. 2. After the 6th launch...
2a) IF you cannot fuel another 1-3-3-3 ship, THEN begin fueling before moving to next farm
2b) ELSE move immediately to next farm without beginning to fuel next rocket
3. When you switch farms, always switch to the egg type that can fuel the least amount of missions. (Obviously, right?)
IMPORTANT: On the 5th week, when you are on the dark matter egg farm, fill up and abandon one short voyegger mission. This will ensure you have enough fuel to get through week 7. Trust me.

And that’s it! Following those steps will bring you 11 care-free weeks of exhen cycling! If you are willing to switch your farm twice on a weekend instead of just once, you can get even farther than 10 weeks. Info will be posted on the Google Sheet soon!

