ENBEC Cycle
ENBEC Cycle

Once you have this cycle set up, the only rules to follow are:

If you have 1T Tachyon left in the tank, switch to Tachyon farm
If you have 3T or less of Dilithium, Antimatter or Dark matter, switch to that farm
This allows you to have your tank fueling activated all the time and easily see when you have to switch farm. Since you always have at least 1T eggs left, it's also rounding-proof !

To kickstart the cycle (disable tank fueling before removing eggs):

Fill the tank with Antimatter
Remove 50%
Fill the tank with Darkmatter
