Fill the tank with Tachyon
Repeatedly remove 50% Tachyon until you have 1T
Fuel and abort 2 short henerprises
Fill the tank with Dilithium
Switch to a Tachyon farm, activate tank fueling and start launching exhens!
Note: I ended up with 30 different valid cycles. I arbitrarily picked the satisfying 5 which fuel Tachyon -> Dilithium -> Antimatter -> Dark Matter, in that order, then picked the one which seemed the easiest to kickstart

