Rounding-safe; always has at least 1T extra of each egg.
Can be modified to add other fuels for short chicken heavy's or ASC in place of excess eggs while cycling, especially on larger fuel tanks
Doesn't get messed up by sending short henerprises for dubcaps in the middle
Setup

Fill your tank with 10% Dilithium, 40% Antimatter, and 50% Dark Matter using the sliders.
Prestige and build a tachyon farm
Set your sliders for Dilithium, Antimatter, and Dark Matter to 50% of your tank (the same as the amount of Dark Matter you filled in step 1) and your slider for Tachyon to half of that.
Turn on Fueling and tanking and start launching hens.
Once you're up and running, switch to the next egg when your tank doesn't fill up all the way because of the slider cap.

The cycle will run Tachyon -> Dilithium -> Antimatter -> Dark Matter and the next egg will also be the one that you have the least of.

