Golden Eggs can be obtained from:

The Shop, via in-app purchases.
Drones, giving Golden Egg}}3, Golden Egg}}6, or Golden Egg}}12 for regular drones, Golden Egg}}12 or 48 for elite drones, in addition to Golden Egg}}96 or Golden Egg}}192 with Drone Rewards.
These values are significantly increased once the player has spent at least Golden Egg}}152,000 total on anything in the game.
This tool can be used to more or less predict how efficient your drone farming will be.
