Grain Silos, or simply Silos, are used for earning Bocks, gaining chickens from Internal Hatcheries, and collecting Boost Tokens while offline. Each silo adds a base of one stored hour of income. For information on Silos for the Path of Virtue, see the Egg of Resilience page.

The number of silos one can build is dependent on their Permit. A Standard Permit allows for 2 silos, while a Pro Permit allows for 10 silos. Silos also have two qualities: with the Standard Permit, offline income is earned at half the online rate, while with the Pro Permit, offline income is earned at the same rate as online.

