Upgrades
Silo Capacity
Silo Capacity allows you to increase the away-time by six minutes per level. There are twenty levels, maxing out at an additional two hours per silo. This brings your total away time to 3 hours per silo with this Epic Research maxed, for a maximum away time of 30 Hours with 10 Silos and maxed out Epic Research.

Silo Quality
As of version 1.9, silo quality no longer can be upgraded through Epic Research. The Pro Permit will automatically grant the user full quality silos, whereas with Standard Permit, you will only get half quality.

