Trivia
Portal Hab
Portal Hab

The model of the Warehouse is used in a number of places, including Center and Eggkea.
Eggkea is a parody of IKEA, a furniture company. It is also evident from the blue color scheme and yellow text.
Purchasing a Planet Portal may use more of your device's resources. If you experience lag, this can be resolved by switching to Low-Performance Mode.
The door to the Planet Portal is a circle by default. If the game detects your device struggling, it'll switch to a triangle. The triangle has fewer polygons to render, easing the burden on your device.
Before factoring in research, a Chicken Universe has exactly 2.4 million times the capacity of a Coop.
Prior to update 1.5 the highest hab was the "Portal" hab.
