Mechanics
The Piggy Bank increases by a number of Golden Eggs every time something is upgraded or purchased.

You can crack it for USD5.99, £5.79, AUD$9.99 or €6.49 each time, which will reset the counter to 0 and give you all the Golden Eggs inside. Contract goals and the Daily Gift Calendar may also add Golden Eggs to the Piggy Bank and even double it. There is a special event which reduces the price by 33%.

Bonuses
Each time the Piggy Bank is cracked it gains a bonus, starting at 2% on the first level, 25% on the second level, and 10n+10% after that point (e.g. level 6 would have a 70% bonus). In other words, starting at level, multiply the contents of the piggy by (n+11)/10.

Piggy Cap
At a certain point, the Piggy Bank fills up and cannot be incremented by buying things. This is a soft cap, though, and the Piggy Bank can still be increased with contract or Daily Gift Calendar rewards.

Prior to level 10, the cap is Golden Egg}}10,000n-2500 where n is piggy level
At level 10 and up, the cap is Golden Egg}}45,000+5,000n, where n is piggy level.
