Piggy Fill Formula
Credit to discord user @toffepeer1 (374952941863305229) on the Main Egg, Inc. discord server for this formula. Original post can be found here.

The way piggy fill works is each action listed below gives a base value, the game then applies a formula also listed below to the base value, which gives the amount of 'raw' piggy (without level, ULTRA and event bonus). This is only relevant when your piggy is not full, which is right after it's cracked, or during an unlimited piggy fill event.

Action	Base Piggy Fill
Research	+3 Golden Egg}}
Purchase Vehicle	+20 Golden Egg}}
Purchase Boost	+25 Golden Egg}}
Purchase Hab	+50 Golden Egg}}
Consume or Demote Artifact	+50 Golden Egg}}
Purchase Rocket	+100 Golden Egg}}
Craft Artifact	+250 Golden Egg}}
Slot Stone	+500 Golden Egg}}
