Buy cheap boosts, specifically bulbs. Buy them one at a time. 1 click of buying 5 nets the same amount of piggy as buying 1. You can buy multiple different boosts at the same time.
Prestige a bit to make use of the rest of the event, however this only gives you maybe 5% of what consuming should of given, so its not that big of a priority.
General tips
Following the list of actions in the table above, you want to have a high volume of "actions" with the limited time you have during the event. The best way to do that is through mass demotion/consumption of artifacts.
You will experience a lot of lag/freezing when you hit consume all on the artifacts; once you click confirm, let the app do its thing and don't click on anything else, or else your phone might crash and it may cause you to lose the artifacts without anything in return. If the lag is too severe, consuming artifacts in halves might ease the lag a bit.
If Kev (the developer of the game) begins to introduce shorter unlimited piggy events, it may be wise to demote all your artifacts beforehand, so that you are wasting less time on laggy demotion, however of course you will have a reduced amount of interactions, use your discretion on your phone specs / previous piggy events experience to make the call yourself.
The past 2 Unlimited Piggy events have been 30 minutes as opposed to the previous 1 hour as of the 18th of March, 2024. Therefore, the advice above should be strongly considered.
The bulk of the piggy comes from consuming fragments, but you gain a lot of those fragments through consuming artifacts, hence the order.
From observations in the first event, T1 books gave the most T1 shells, which gave the most piggy; if you want to solely focus on making that bank, you could focus BoB Exliners.
Buying boosts also costs GE to purchase, the only profitable boost is the warming bulb.
Trivia
The piggy bank used to cost $2.99, £2.99, or €2.99 but this was changed on 14 July 2019 after the $1 piggy sale. It was increased again with the Contracts v2 update on May 1st, 2023.
A piggy at level 9 will give you exactly double due to the +100% level bonus
Roughly until the 27th of March 2024, the piggy formula for levels <10 was Golden Egg}}7,500+1,000n
